  "description": "Maximum competition ecology (competitionStrength=0.9) between Square src1 and Sine src2. An LFO sweeps srcMix continuously — as the mix shifts, whichever source has more amplitude becomes the temporary predator. The other recedes, only to surge back when the cycle turns. Population dynamics made audible: one dominates, the other survives, then they reverse. Classic Lotka-Volterra behaviour in a synth.",
